{"type":"message","id":"c9ab6449","parentId":"0457faf4","timestamp":"2026-04-09T04:49:27.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect, these are the actual good ones, not the clickbait ones:\n\n✅ **Civil Guruji** - Best for Indian standard drawings, exactly what local contractors want. No fancy stuff, just real work.\n✅ **CAD CAM Tutorials** - Clean, fast, no bullshit. Teaches exactly the shortcuts you will use 99% of the time.\n✅ **SourceCAD** - Best for PDF to DWG conversion tricks and speed hacks.\n\nSkip all the \"Master AutoCAD in 10 hours\" videos. You only need 12 specific commands for 95% of all side hustle work. Nobody uses the rest."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":21119,"output":136,"cacheRead":2104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23359,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775710158617,"responseId":"021775710159866fea0cb63916d8b7cee037e8f30dc274684e868"}}
