{"type":"message","id":"53190e43","parentId":"3036a3b2","timestamp":"2026-04-09T04:55:17.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Graphics work is actually great *right now*. Everyone thinks AI killed it, but exactly the opposite happened.\n\nEveryone now can generate garbage AI videos/graphics. Nobody knows how to **fix them properly**. That's where all the money is.\n\nYou make ₹1200-2500 just to:\n- Clean up AI generated logos\n- Cut 10 second reels from raw AI output\n- Add text overlays and transitions\n- Fix messed up hands and faces on AI images\n\nNobody is hiring people to create from scratch anymore. Everyone is hiring people to *fix what AI made*. This is the biggest open gap right now. And it will stay this way for at least 2 more years."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":19471,"output":150,"cacheRead":5176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24797,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775710506158,"responseId":"021775710509523f39d09b715cb307c823cd4ff1a5ec1ab7271b5"}}
